{"tid":2212435,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支持新巴970司機","createTime":"2020-09-21T21:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T21:39:33.000Z","uid":323449,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e744480f8777f4a50ce4bccb2a75952378aa575e","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:10:44.000Z","msg":"出事前半小時的彌敦道,無王法.<br />\n為杜絕游行隊伍的形成,警方把彌敦道斬開一節節,每隔百米就有警員拉橙帶,把剛巧路過的市民封住起碼一個鐘.其他好彩啱啱未被納入封鎖線的市民,則可以打橫打直打斜兼紅燈之下,自由行,過馬路.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLXJY6x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLXJY6x.png&h=5e430e2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cab5dd4ad77b8e666b4b17a9119b44bf426375e","tid":2212435,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810bc5dc8d6ff3d0bcbd35cf8f765afe0b5c4322","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:14:15.000Z","msg":"不單佔據巴士埋線.更不時越過中線.只為拘留部份市民在行人路上,他們自己則徵用馬路給自己企.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL3hi6X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL3hi6X.png&h=37e8a327&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e5bb5f9f5fe8c4878fc2785b97f8ece94b72af1","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:19:58.000Z","msg":"新巴970 尚有三鐘才駛至此處.<br />\n但可看見警察直播他們自己霸佔了兩條行車線.被拘留在橙帶內的市民,無事做,只好席地而坐.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUwVQe2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUwVQe2.png&h=c2ee8662&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d9078987231eccb0f2cf50ddc310769a0631936","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:21:46.000Z","msg":"再比多張相大家.睇清楚,出事前兩分鐘的路面情況.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVVSSuZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVVSSuZ.png&h=ed47adbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b3316500584eae070b5bf134bebdc48710cdafe","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:23:48.000Z","msg":"一輛警車.打橫泊了兩條線.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WFC3Cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WFC3Cd.png&h=b6ecc8b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1350430f3e3d838a31129c613347effd32a064c","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:27:41.000Z","msg":"紅燈,但只要好彩,行早一步,或行遲一步,未被拘留在橙帶內的其餘所有人,都在警察視而不見的情況下,自由行.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YK72via.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYK72via.png&h=fc5be940&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a745f0036b6bdf8c48f5202bb76684583d0d0414","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:30:04.000Z","msg":"這是警察直播,至19秒轉移到對面馬路(啱啱咁Q),新巴970隨即駛至,而未被拍攝到.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3s2vjz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3s2vjz.png&h=aa9a3ae8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77b092507a3c834908bf5db2055c0716de4e721d","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:36:40.000Z","msg":"新巴970 剛剛駛過,警察直播中,聽到有車响咹三秒.可能每按一下只响一秒,但,總之,只响了三秒.警察直播鏡頭即拉回南行線,此時可見該段馬路的情況,佔路的警察,並無意識&lt;有罪行發生&gt;,而是閒企.無無聊聊的.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evWuUOq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevWuUOq.png&h=c336a33d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c22919f2a70206e2edaeebe7a1643d4e9784def","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:46:10.000Z","msg":"突有一個,作&quot;速龍&quot;打扮的便衣(非速龍正常製服),頭盔上貼了三柴以資識別.在警察直播中,可聽到他/他們叫通訊,要求截停一輛巴,但有人不識英文字母.一兩秒後才搞清楚巴士車牌.然後,作&quot;速龍&quot;打扮的便衣,奔跑去追巴士.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HY03Zid.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHY03Zid.png&h=7b2afcbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0466e087ea70b555d477fe754d504a38e3942fa5","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:51:12.000Z","msg":"作&quot;速龍&quot;打扮的便衣,在彌敦道上奔跑所過,左邊有大叔,右邊有清潔婆婆.(有人可以分柝一下,巴士如何在這樣的馬路上,正常行走?)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6U8qZc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6U8qZc.png&h=8ad3a60d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69ab5741c660c02441987aa84edcbf26769b69db","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SHmL0n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SHmL0n.png&h=f54c2c89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dff7ef154446466ec9f7c53534b6c2c827c0444","tid":2212435,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87205dfb9dc1ab42509c4f270b3ea11608659d41","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:53:53.000Z","msg":"巴士未能埋站落客.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hmZxFD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hmZxFD.png&h=9a8b049c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76c1f161f36af7cce8744a667e53d5ce6a576094","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:55:32.000Z","msg":"作&quot;速龍&quot;打扮人士,繼續追巴士..<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0Xqtew.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0Xqtew.png&h=8f2d3aed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb30cbfbdff2a7449e7c5e63a973d142567cdab5","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ye2uatj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYe2uatj.png&h=1784f698&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0120d5ca2d83150569a3ab947a04c66c841cf764","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T21:58:42.000Z","msg":"追到了,用了三十多秒.(世界男子150米紀錄係15秒).<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mL7BzVC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmL7BzVC.png&h=9d97fce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSiUmAH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSiUmAH.png&h=6913d4e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GcgKJO7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGcgKJO7.png&h=11764d90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"027e685867d33d39fe4fc002253c3f57e0a8520f","tid":2212435,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T22:00:30.000Z","msg":"隻發瘟狗癲狗症發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到司機戴豬嘴就狂追"},{"pid":"b6abc9293b57104d0a877359be32c909e9e951d3","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T22:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/maLGL2O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmaLGL2O.png&h=7e876949&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n加入蘋果直播的另一鏡頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RsC2vuN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRsC2vuN.jpg&h=de6a9fe5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n帶槍上車拉人.軍伙不應登入車箱的.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pjFzmB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjFzmB2.jpg&h=5b3b53c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"878e503568eb13f8ac913af6fd178f56daa1ae1e","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T22:06:18.000Z","msg":"司機被即時帶落車.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5miOh5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5miOh5.png&h=84fad801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/me72vwu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fme72vwu.png&h=9b4ac398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eauDOib.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeauDOib.png&h=24ff0ec4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83d89f8853755ce3fa960a337a1e3e7076b99049","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T22:09:53.000Z","msg":"司機立正受查,企得比警察直.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7hBuUZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7hBuUZa.png&h=45e5aa9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2GKJSB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2GKJSB.png&h=8e5da64f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b03193d2d0072d4c0bc69756e88bd6f8ffae6e15","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T22:25:43.000Z","msg":"警察直播員兩分鐘後&quot;斷定&quot;有人不適當响咹,指司機挑釁警方,影响執法.所以截停調查.<br />\n一兩分鐘後.鏡頭見到一只&quot;黑手&quot;,把一個時沙叫過來&quot;指導&quot;..而背境另有一名高級警司無所是事.<br />\n如無意外,該黑手屬於早前在文明里叫通訊,要求截停巴士,本身作&quot;速龍&quot;打扮的便衣三柴警長,現場只有他穿長袖黑衫帶大面手錶.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEVoe4q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEVoe4q.png&h=cb629ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PD5GMa9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPD5GMa9.png&h=bb3b90bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KcHmMbb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcHmMbb.png&h=b3ab5e8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be99a7ab359c65ad10b417ee9ef79e4bda7d224d","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T22:33:28.000Z","msg":"然後,該名受到&quot;黑手&quot;特別訓示的時沙,走回司機前面,以誇張的兇狠的身體及口部語言,指控司&quot;你係謀殺!我地而家要票控你,因為你的駕駛行為,我地會票控你,你考牌有講架麻,個响號咁用既咩?唔係咁用架,唔係你覺得就係法律,法律就係法律,明白未!&quot; (無錯,原文炒錄).<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8v2mMdY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8v2mMdY.png&h=e94d82ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuoUmNk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuoUmNk.png&h=a605836a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CiR6XkH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCiR6XkH.png&h=028ffb0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4eeaffc18e2f9adb0f156dd72ac94b007dcae00e","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T22:45:42.000Z","msg":"總結<br />\n警方到處封鎖行人路,把行人分化.被封鎖拘留的,無所是事或坐人或企,玩電話,東張西望.總之,失去自由.<br />\n另一邊.差一步,未被封鎖的市民,隨意橫過馬路,跨出行人路自由行.手推垃圾車無路可行,惟有走出馬路行.三線其中兩線,一左一右,被人佔用,警察甚至佔去1.5條線.剩下0.5條線予巴士,是不是太過份呢? &quot;被太貼近&quot;呢?<br />\n做成這樣危險的環境.係警方.<br />\n司機响咹提醒走在馬路上的人,就被控犯法.香港不單止失法,根本連規矩都被打爛."},{"pid":"6f59e4c5de97f8473043c9f73f60a70cf11b385f","tid":2212435,"uid":323449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:02:46.000Z","msg":"一定要支持新巴司機.<br />\n不可接受這樣的屈辱."}],"pinned":{"pid":"518858726ba2b3300e22d706744e00cf65ecdab7","tid":2212435,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T06:24:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，好大機會包括<strong><sp